<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>여론조사 목록</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container mt-4">
    <div class="row mb-4">
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <h1>여론조사 목록</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 text-end">
        <a href="/polls/new" class="btn btn-primary">새 여론조사 만들기</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <% if (polls && polls.length > 0) { %>
      <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2 row-cols-lg-3 g-4">
        <% polls.forEach(poll => { %>
          <div class="col">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title"><%= poll.title %></h5>
                <% if (poll.description) { %>
                  <p class="card-text text-muted"><%= poll.description %></p>
                <% } %>
                <p class="card-text">
                  <small class="text-muted">
                    옵션 <%= poll.options.length %>개 | 총 <%= poll.options.reduce((sum, opt) => sum + opt.votes, 0) %> 투표
                  </small>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="card-footer bg-transparent">
                <a href="/polls/<%= poll._id %>" class="btn btn-outline-primary w-100">투표하기</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% }) %>
      </div>
    <% } else { %>
      <div class="alert alert-info">
        아직 생성된 여론조사가 없습니다. 첫 번째 여론조사를 만들어보세요!
      </div>
    <% } %>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>